Result types in cli/output/result.go. Sealed interface (unexported isResult method). Concrete types: TodoResult{State}, ListResult{State,Verbose,SpecContents,MarkerContents}, ShowResult{IsSpec,ID,Spec,Marker,Content,LinkedSpecs,LinkedMarkers,OutboundRefs,InboundRefs}, DiffEdgeResult{Result}, DiffExpandedResult{ID,Edges}, DiffAllResult{State,Edges}, OkResult{Command,Message}, ErrorResult{Command,Message,Hint,Exit}, TextResult{Text}, VersionResult{Version}. ShowResult carries inbound/outbound ref lists (computed from baseline Refs in BuildShowResult) so presenters can render the spec's rhizomatic neighborhood. ShowResult and ListResult carry pre-resolved content so presenters stay pure (no I/O).